  "summary": "Malicious code in pycacheopt (PyPI)",
  "details": "The extension module hides code that in specific circumstances executes given code. The malicious action is hidden only in the extension module with the same-named Python code file containing only benign code.\n\nThis campaign was first detected by Aikido Security.\n\n\n---\n\nCategory: MALICIOUS - The campaign has clearly malicious intent, like infostealers.\n\n\nCampaign: 2026-05-pycacheopt\n\n\nReasons (based on the campaign):\n\n\n - other\n\n\n - The package contains code to detect if it is running in a sandbox environment.\n\n",
